OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine, dry
OL,6,Fand sunny evening for most. Any
OL,7,Fisolated showers soon easing. Cloud
OL,8,Fdeveloping across eastern coasts, but
OL,9,Fremaining clear for most. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA bright start away from
OL,12,Feastern coasts. Cloud then building
OL,13,Finto the early afternoon, followed by
OL,14,Fanother bright end to the day. Slight
OL,15,Fchance of isolated showers. Light
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
