OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FRemaining warm with light winds, Fine
OL,7,Fand dry on Sunday but with cloud
OL,8,Fincreasing through Monday and Tuesday,
OL,9,FPotential for coastal drizzle in the
OL,10,Feast.
